## 1. Project Overview

**hmpsn.studio** is an SEO/web analytics platform built with **React 19 + Vite 8 + TailwindCSS 4 + React Router DOM 7** (frontend) and **Express + TypeScript** (backend). It manages client websites via Webflow, Google Search Console, GA4, and SEMRush integrations.

- **Routing** â€” **React Router DOM 7** (`src/routes.ts` defines `Page` + `ClientTab` types, `adminPath()` + `clientPath()` helpers). Admin: `/ws/:workspaceId/:tab?`, Client: `/client/:workspaceId/:tab?`, global tabs: `/settings`, `/roadmap`, `/prospect`, `/ai-usage`.
- **API Client** â€” Typed fetch wrappers in `src/api/` (7 modules). All components import from `src/api/` â€” no raw `fetch()` calls in components. `ApiError` class with `.status` for error handling.
- **Shared Types** â€” `shared/types/` (11 modules) shared between client and server. Canonical interfaces for workspace, analytics, content, payments, approvals, schema-plan, etc.
- **Storage** â€” **SQLite** via `better-sqlite3` (WAL mode, foreign keys ON) at `DATA_BASE/dashboard.db`. 21 migrations merged to `main` â€” 95+ server modules use SQLite. See Â§ 2a below.
- **AI** â€” OpenAI GPT-4.1/4.1-mini/4.1-nano via `server/openai-helpers.ts` (`callOpenAI`), Anthropic Claude via `server/anthropic-helpers.ts` (`callAnthropic`) for creative prose
- **Payments** â€” Stripe Checkout (not Payment Intents). Config encrypted on disk (AES-256-GCM). Admin UI for keys + products.
- **Auth** â€” Dual system: internal JWT (7-day, admin) + client JWT (24h, per-workspace). Legacy shared-password still supported. Turnstile CAPTCHA on client login/forgot-password (optional).
- **Validation** â€” **Zod v3** (`server/middleware/validate.ts`) for Express request body validation. Schemas declared per-route, middleware returns structured 400 errors.
- **Caching** â€” **React Query** (`@tanstack/react-query`) for all frontend data fetching/caching. `QueryClientProvider` in `main.tsx`. **Migration complete** (4 phases shipped) â€” entire frontend uses React Query. 50+ hooks in `src/hooks/admin/` and `src/hooks/client/`. Query key prefixes: `client-*`, `admin-ga4-*`, `admin-gsc-*`, `admin-workspace-*`, `admin-audit-*`, `admin-posts`, `admin-briefs`.
- **Compression** â€” `compression` middleware in `server/app.ts` for gzip responses.
- **Monetization** â€” 3 tiers (Free/Growth/Premium), per-item content purchases, 14-day Growth trial, UX soft-gating via `<TierGate>`
- **Logging** â€” **Pino** structured JSON logging (`server/logger.ts`). `createLogger(module)` for child loggers. Pretty-print in dev, JSON in prod.
- **Error monitoring** â€” **Sentry** (`server/sentry.ts` + frontend `@sentry/react`). Auto-tags errors with `workspaceId`. Conditional source maps.
- **CI/CD** â€” GitHub Actions (`.github/workflows/ci.yml` for lint/test/build, `e2e.yml` for Playwright, `security.yml` for weekly npm audit).
- **Graceful shutdown** â€” SIGTERM/SIGINT handlers: flush email/AI/SEMRush queues, mark running jobs as interrupted, close DB, close WebSocket. Reentrancy guard.
- **Backups** â€” Local periodic backups + optional S3 off-site upload (`BACKUP_S3_BUCKET`).

